Function Fibonacci Integer iNum Returns Integer
    Integer iNum1 iNum2
    
    If (iNum = 0)
    Function_Return 0
    If (iNum = 1)
    Function_Return 1
    
    Get Fibonacci (iNum - 1) to iNum1
    Get Fibonacci (iNum - 2) to iNum2
    
    Function_Return (iNum1 + iNum2)
End_Function

Procedure TestFibonacci
    Integer iResult
    
    Get Fibonacci 30 to iResult
    
    Send Info_Box iResult "Fibonacci"
End_Procedure

Send TestFibonacci
